Displays the menu for airline-\/specific statistics options. 

This method prints the airline statistics menu to the console, allowing users to choose between different statistical options related to a specific airline. The displayed menu includes corresponding numeric options, and users can enter their choice. The menu covers information such as the number of flights operated by the airline, the number of destinations served, and options to return to the statistics menu or the main menu. 

